 2020-04012020-05-30,  ,  ,  GAC, 
ActUnited Nations Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Regulations Implementing the United Nations Resolutions on Somalia
PrecisRegulations amending the REGULATIONS IMPLEMENTING THE UNITED NATIONS RESOLUTIONS ON SOMALIA in order to (1) fulfill Canada's international legal obligation to implement the binding decisions of the Security Council set out in Resolutions 2111 (2013), and 2498 (2019); and (2) address miscellaneous amendments raised by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations.
